                <p>
               <pb/>
               <hi rend="italic">New Holland.</hi> –The Government intend to move <lb/>in the House of Commons the grant of t1000, to de<lb break="no"/>fray a portion of the charge of an expedition, to be de<lb break="no"/>spatched for the purpose of " exploring the north-west <lb/>part of New Holland," agreeably to recommendations <lb/>of the Royal Geographical Society, "to ascertain the <lb/>existence, or the contrary, of any great river" in the <lb/>north-west portion of New Holland.</p>
            </body>
